== 計分板故障 ==
在第二天， 球場角落的[[電子記分牌|電子記分牌]]在兩人打至47-47時，更一度出現故障而需用人手記分。<ref name="nyt-logistics">{{cite news |title=Logistics Are Put to the Test at Wimbledon |author=John Martin |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2010-06-23 |url=http://straightsets.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/06/23/logistics-are-put-to-the-test-at-wimbledon/ |accessdate=2010-06-25 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111201736/https://straightsets.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/06/23/logistics-are-put-to-the-test-at-wimbledon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 官方網站上的線上計分板在局數超過50-50之後，從0-0開始計算<ref>{{cite web |title=John Isner and Nicolas Mahut Marathon Match Suspended for Darkness at Wimbledon |author=Michael Hurley |work=NESN.com |publisher={{link-en|New England Sports Network|New England Sports Network}} |date=2010-06-23 |url=http://www.nesn.com/2010/06/john-isner-nicolas-mahut-locked-in-marathon-match-at-wimbledon.html |accessdate=2010-06-25 |archive-date=2012-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224054251/http://www.nesn.com/2010/06/john-isner-nicolas-mahut-locked-in-marathon-match-at-wimbledon.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。IBM工作人員對18號球場的計分板進行維修直到晚上11:45，以適應比賽第三天的比分。據工程師說，如果第三天雙方又打至少25局，記分板又會故障。<ref name="martin20100624">Martin, John. "[http://straightsets.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/06/24/live-analysis-isner-mahut-to-resume-historic-match/?src=mv Scoreboard tuneup] {{Wayback|url=http://straightsets.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/06/24/live-analysis-isner-mahut-to-resume-historic-match/?src=mv |date=20201109105338 }}" ''The New York Times'', {{Nowrap|24 June}} 2010.</ref>

